---
/**
 * /admin — landing redirect. Single admin tool today (license
 * requests), so `/admin` just bounces there. When we add more
 * tools we'll grow this into an index page.
 *
 * Middleware has already verified the admin session by the time we
 * reach this file; an unauthorized visitor never sees the redirect.
 */
return Astro.redirect('/admin/license-requests');
